#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.left_shift.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.left\\_shift"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.lshift.lshift:1 of
msgid "Shift the bits of an integer to the left."
msgstr "将整数的位向左移动。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.lshift.lshift:3 of
msgid ""
"Bits are shifted to the left by appending `x2` 0s at the right of `x1`. "
"Since the internal representation of numbers is in binary format, this "
"operation is equivalent to multiplying `x1` by ``2**x2``."
msgstr ""
"通过在 `x1` 的右侧附加 `x2` 个 0 来将位向左移动。由于数字的内部表示是"
"二进制格式，此操作等效于将 `x1` 乘以 ``2**x2``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.lshift.lshift of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.lshift.lshift:7 of
msgid "Input values."
msgstr "输入值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.lshift.lshift:9 of
msgid "Number of zeros to append to `x1`. Has to be non-negative."
msgstr "要附加到 `x1` 的零的数量。必须为非负数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.lshift.lshift:11 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"存储结果的位置。如果提供，它必须具有与输入广播兼容的形状。如果未提供或为 "
"`None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（只能作为关键字参数）的长度必须等于"
"输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.lshift.lshift:16 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.lshift.lshift of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.lshift.lshift:21 of
msgid "**out** -- Return `x1` with bits shifted `x2` times to the left."
msgstr "**out** -- 返回将 `x1` 的位向左移动 `x2` 次的结果。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.lshift.lshift of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.lshift.lshift:26 of
msgid ":py:obj:`right_shift`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.lshift.lshift:27 of
msgid "Shift the bits of an integer to the right."
msgstr "将整数的位向右移动。"

